{"tid":1168683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"性感幼稚園老師引暴動 網民重點全錯放火辣身材！！","createTime":"2019-05-24T00:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T01:46:48.000Z","uid":30186,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"794a75d63f57bf4681ebefa99d8e05f8b70c80b4","tid":1168683,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"網民：我要親自接送小孩上課！<br />\n<br />\n近日幾張幼稚園老師蹲在路邊幫孩子們整理衣物的相片在網上瘋傳，而這全因一眾男網民放錯重點，將焦點放在了女老師火辣的身材和姿勢上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6hWQOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6hWQOk.png&h=113f3e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fgwEGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fgwEGG.png&h=22c5fc18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從相片中可見，一名長髮女老師穿著白色制服，黑短褲及高跟鞋，蹲在地上貼心地替小朋友整理服裝儀容。由於蹲姿讓女老師窈窕的身材更加明顯，一眾男性瞬間把視線轉移到性感的女老師身上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WMkx1P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WMkx1P.png&h=ba6b0319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實該女老師來自越南，是當地一間幼稚園老師。有網民甚至找出了女老師的日常照，發現她更有著甜美的長相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSm8GVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSm8GVh.png&h=e49ccf84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後男網民都紛紛留言直呼：「害我想重讀了」、「爸爸可能每天準時接小孩」、「我會每天親自接送小孩上課」、「來去越南考察一下」、「我以後要當園長」、「走了！報名幼稚園了」、「一起入學吧，活到老學到老啊」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4391293-性感幼稚園老師引暴動-網民重點全錯放火辣身材！/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4391293-%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%BC%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E5%85%A8%E9%8C%AF%E6%94%BE%E7%81%AB%E8%BE%A3%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90%EF%BC%81%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a468e10f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4391293-性感幼稚園老師引暴動-網民重點全錯放火辣身材！/</a>"},{